ActFishing and Recreational Harbours Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the FISHING AND RECREATIONAL HARBOURS REGULATIONS by removing 128 harbour locations that have already been legally transferred/divested to other organizations from Schedule I. The amendments will also change the name of one harbour in Quebec from “Havre-St-Pierre - Fishermen’s Section and Ramp” to “Havre-St-Pierre”.
